title: MusicXML Song Complexity Prediction

title: Goodreads Book Recommender
description: Personalized book recommendation system for Goodreads users, a Cornac BPR model was optimized with latent factor tuning and regularization, ranking 16th out of 711 competitors on private leaderboard.

title: Food.com Recipe Analysis
description: Analyzed the relationship between recipe ratings and attributes such as preparation time, ingredients, and steps using multiple linear regression and ridge regression.
